entries.femaleVariant: You know, I did! "Home Again." Preem BD, super chill.
Ah, cool. What's it about? Action? Comedy?
None of the above. You're a vet, just got back from the war. Haven't been home for five years. Got your wife, kids, dog all waitin' for you at the airport.
Yeah, exactly. And I got all those reductions going on in my team, so a little escape is good.
Ehhh, yeah, know what you mean.
